title: Vermont Center for Geographic Information, DSL Systems, Vermont, 2006
name: Vermont Center for Geographic Information, DSL Systems, Vermont, 2006
description:
Abstract: The VT DSL Broadband System dataset (DSL2006) includes polygons depicting the extent of Vermont's DSL broadband system as of 12/31/2006.
      This data layer is an updated version of DSL2003.
      
    Purpose:  To represent the extent of Vermont's DSL Broadband System as of 12/31/2006.
Please search for Vermont-GIS for more   local level GIS datasets.
